#	Chromosome 10

	The tricky subject of psychoneuroimmunology is explored by Paul Martin’s _The sickening mind_ (Harper Collins, 1997).
	1. Martin, P. (1997). _The sickening mind: brain, behaviour, immunity and disease._ Harper Collins, London.
	2. Becker, J. B., Breedlove, M. S. and Crews, D. (1992). _Behavioral endocrinology._ MIT Press, Cambridge, Massachusetts.
