	4. Wurtman, R. J. and Wurtman, J. J. (1994). Carbohydrates and depression. In Masters, R. D. and McGuire, M. T. (eds), _The neurotransmitter revolution_, pp. 96–109. Southern Illinois University Press, Carbondale and Edwardsville.
