#	Chromosome 15

	Wolf Reik and Azim Surani’s _Genomic imprinting_ (Oxford University Press, 1997) is a good collection of essays on the topic of imprinting. Many books explore gender differences including my own _The Red Queen_ (Viking, 1993).
